
# Hugging Face Inference API (FREE - No key needed for public models!)
# Popular models:
#   - facebook/detr-resnet-50 (80 COCO objects) - Recommended, faster
#   - facebook/detr-resnet-101 (80 COCO objects) - More accurate
#   - XintongHan/rt-detr-coco-1x (80 COCO objects) - Real-time optimized
#   - facebook/detr-resnet-101-panoptic (panoptic segmentation)
# Get free token (optional) at: https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
HUGGINGFACE_API_TOKEN=
HUGGINGFACE_MODEL=facebook/detr-resnet-50
